# LazyGolf

> A multi-vertical golf lifestyle brand combining apparel, technology platform, and entertainment content for casual golfers who don't take the game too seriously.

---

## Overview

LazyGolf is the flagship venture of [[Kikman Enterprises]], targeting the underserved market of casual, fun-focused golfers. Unlike traditional golf brands that emphasize performance and prestige, LazyGolf embraces the laid-back approach to the game.

**Tagline Ideas:**
- "Golf for the rest of us"
- "Swing lazy, score happy"
- "Less effort, more fun"

---

