## Go-to-Market Strategy

### Phase 1: Brand Building (Q1-Q2 2025)
- Launch social media presence
- Release inaugural YouTube video
- Build email list with waitlist
- Develop initial apparel designs

### Phase 2: Apparel Launch (Q2-Q3 2025)
- Launch e-commerce store
- Limited initial product run
- Influencer seeding (golf TikTok/Instagram)
- Content marketing (YouTube + social)

### Phase 3: Platform Beta (Q3-Q4 2025)
- Soft launch to friends and family
- Collect feedback, iterate
- Public beta launch
- Focus on league organizers as champions

### Phase 4: Scale (2026+)
- Expand product line
- Platform premium features
- Partnership opportunities
- Potential retail distribution

